                <br><br>
                In May 2018 at F8, the company announced it would offer its own dating service. Shares in competitor
                Match Group fell by 22%. Facebook Dating includes privacy features and friends are unable to view
                their friends' dating profile. In July, Facebook was charged £500,000 by UK watchdogs for failing
