                In January 2019, the 10-year challenge was started asking users to post a photograph of themselves
                from 10 years ago (2009) and a more recent photo.
                <br><br>
                Criticized for its role in vaccine hesitancy, Facebook announced in March 2019 that it would provide
                users with "authoritative information" on the topic of vaccines. A study in the journal
                Vaccine of advertisements posted in the three months prior to that found that 54% of the
