                Demographics
                The highest number of Facebook users as of October 2018 are from India and the United States, followed
                by Indonesia, Brazil and Mexico. Region-wise, the highest number of users are from Asia-Pacific
                (947 million) followed by Europe (381 million) and US-Canada (242 million). The rest of the world has
                750 million users.

                Over the 2008–2018 period, the percentage of users under 34 declined to less than half of the
                total.

